OL,3,CMan jailed for 19 years after
OL,4,C'slashing' adopted mother's throat
OL,6,FA man from Nottinghamshire has been
OL,7,Fjailed after attacking his adopted
OL,8,Fmother and slashing her throat.
OL,10,FLee Bates, 52, was heavily intoxicated
OL,11,Fwhen he attacked the 81-year-old
OL,12,Fvictim at their home in Mill Road,
OL,13,FNewthorpe on 6 June last year.
OL,15,FNottingham Crown Court heard he pushed
OL,16,Fhis mother to the floor before
OL,17,Fstamping on her neck and causing her
OL,18,Fto lose consciousness.
