OL,3,CMan jailed for 19 years after
OL,4,C'slashing' adopted mother's throat
OL,6,FThe woman adopted Bates in the 1970s
OL,7,Ffollowing the death of his birth
OL,8,Fmother.
OL,10,FAfter Bates called the police himself,
OL,11,Fambulance services found the victim in
OL,12,Fa hallway with a slash wound to her
OL,13,Fthroat and a crushed trachea.
OL,15,FBates was charged with attempted
OL,16,Fmurder after ambulance staff witnessed
OL,17,Fhim washing a bloodied knife in a
OL,18,Fkitchen sink moments before his arrest.
