OL,3,CMan jailed for 19 years after
OL,4,C'slashing' adopted mother's throat
OL,6,FBates was sentenced to 19 years and
OL,7,Feight months at Nottingham Crown Court
OL,8,Fon 23 January.
OL,10,F"Bates is a dangerous and violent man"
OL,12,FDetective Inspector James Oakton from
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police, said:
OL,15,F"This was an appalling and sustained
OL,16,Fattack that left an elderly woman with
OL,17,Ftruly terrible injuries.
