OL,3,CMan jailed for 19 years after
OL,4,C'slashing' adopted mother's throat
OL,6,F"Had it not been for the bravery and
OL,7,Fresilience of the ambulance crew and
OL,8,Fattending response who provided
OL,9,Flifesaving care to the victim, her
OL,10,Finjuries could have been fatal.
OL,12,F"I am therefore pleased to learn the
OL,13,Fambulance crew will receive a High
OL,14,FSheriff's Award recognising their
OL,15,Fbravery and life saving intervention.
OL,17,F"The attack left the victim in
OL,18,Fhospital for three weeks and she
OL,19,Fcontinues to endure pain and
OL,20,Fdiscomfort.
OL,26,@nD@AOUyD@AOU
